FISCAL 2012 COMPARED TO FISCAL 2011

EXCLUDING THE CHANGES IN CURRENCY EXCHANGE RATES, REVENUES FOR THE EMERGING MARKETS INCREASED 26% FOR FISCAL 2012 AS ALL TERRITORIES IN THE GEOGRAPHY REPORTED DOUBLE-DIGIT REVENUE GROWTH, LED BY ARGENTINA, BRAZIL, MEXICO AND KOREA.

