THE COMPANY RECOGNIZES INTEREST AND PENALTIES RELATED TO INCOME TAX MATTERS IN INCOME TAX EXPENSE. THE LIABILITY FOR PAYMENT OF INTEREST AND PENALTIES INCREASED

